abstract: Afghanistan's cricket team makes good showing before losing to Sri Lanka by four wickets at World Cup match in Dunedin, New Zealand.
lead_paragraph: The Afghans, competing in their first World Cup, pushed higher-ranked Sri Lanka to the limit before losing by four wickets.

headline.main: Strong Showing by Afghans at World Cup
